Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.78,0:05:40.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  今天是第一次在学校以外的地方和小芽一起玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.75,0:05:47.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「特别」～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.63,0:05:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是在玩  不是在打工吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.61,0:05:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…好了  休息时间结束了  结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.52,0:05:57.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  咦  最轻松自在的不是小芽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.30,0:05:58.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为你们拿来续杯的饮料了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.91,0:06:20.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小睦  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:21.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.55,0:06:22.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.17,0:06:23.62,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛好痛好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.25,0:06:24.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是蜜柑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.62,0:06:26.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在要去你们那边了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:28.60,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛好痛好痛好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.93,0:06:28.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.02,0:06:33.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我刚想接电话  不小心摔了一跤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:36.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稻森同学  你在玩什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:37.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  Shutter Chance
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.18,0:06:41.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请看一看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:45.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在起基本入会免费宣传中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生们放暑假了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.91,0:06:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕她们这么清闲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.27,0:07:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.03,0:07:37.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.07,0:07:43.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假之所以特别  大概是因为它的构成要素很Special
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:44.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,构成要素？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.14,0:07:46.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Special？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.21,0:07:49.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假的电影
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.70,0:07:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是好莱坞的超大作  很Special
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:54.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假的冰淇凌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:56.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能叠上五个  很Special
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:07:58.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连凉面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.59,0:08:00.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是暑假Special菜单
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.35,0:08:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  暑假=特别  证明结束
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.03,0:08:10.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小睦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:12.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都幸苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.23,0:08:13.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么热的天有劳大家了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.33,0:08:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我说  工作根本就没怎么进行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.33,0:08:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.04,0:08:21.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏得小芽都在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.99,0:08:22.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…真没面子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:28.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为这个  我们学生才会被那些打工的小瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.04,0:08:30.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.79,0:08:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没说！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.48,0:08:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  我的那份呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.20,0:08:46.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:49.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水枪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.71,0:08:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  「特别」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.56,0:08:55.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  「特别」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.71,0:08:57.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:08:58.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.16,0:09:00.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没～什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:04.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假  是学生独有的特别的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.13,0:09:07.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作为从事报道工作的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.00,0:09:11.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定继续追寻这份特别
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:13.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进攻！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:15.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.77,0:09:48.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.10,0:09:50.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到零食店了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:51.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.81,0:10:02.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是您的那份
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:08.63,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快速列车马上就要通过了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.15,0:10:12.10,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请退到黄线后等待
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.08,0:10:15.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.21,0:10:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了一身汗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:24.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草莓味的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.04,0:10:25.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抹茶味的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.94,0:10:26.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柠檬味的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.84,0:10:27.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏打味的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.86,0:10:29.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后  我是宇治金时味
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:31.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  很完美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.15,0:10:36.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.45,0:10:37.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:39.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勺子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:41.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:52.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.04,0:11:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄错了换乘列车  光是联络就等了一个半小时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:17.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在暑假期间可以随意乘坐的慢车  学生18号票
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.50,0:11:23.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夜两日的圣樱学生会特别合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:27.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.54,0:11:41.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.84,0:11:47.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都没有预先看一下天气预报吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.12,0:11:50.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按…按照性格来说  这是小芽应该做的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.69,0:11:55.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪  蜜柑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.37,0:11:57.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  刚刚还在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.84,0:11:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咕噜  咕噜  咕噜…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.97,0:12:04.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  蜜柑被吹跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.51,0:12:04.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:06.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  快去救她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.68,0:12:36.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这里连便利店的影子都没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.43,0:12:38.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是…乡下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.64,0:12:41.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在2035年不可能有这种事发生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.73,0:12:44.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  先找住的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.50,0:12:45.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能这么做了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:46.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小睦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.85,0:12:47.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.05,0:12:49.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咕噜  咕噜  咕噜…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.43,0:12:51.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的难道是蜜柑？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.96,0:12:53.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跌进水田里了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.11,0:12:55.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  快去救她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.86,0:13:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.23,0:13:03.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:05.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  真的不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.11,0:13:07.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要担心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:10.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.74,0:13:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.47,0:13:14.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是OK了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.27,0:13:18.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:23.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  钱我已经打进网络帐户里了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:25.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太打扰别人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:29.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有就是  原本计划要去的旅馆我退掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.46,0:13:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:33.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  谢谢  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.68,0:13:36.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了你  我们毫无准备也能直接入住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:39.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.64,0:13:41.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会给别人添麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.39,0:13:43.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正把我们带到房间去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:46.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  嗯  那再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.90,0:13:51.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.93,0:13:55.48,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.65,0:13:57.40,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这种样式的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.00,0:13:55.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在十点结账
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.47,0:13:57.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急出口在二楼的左侧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.41,0:13:59.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娱乐室在一楼的东面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.57,0:14:01.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴室到晚上一点为止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:02.94,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来小芽的最可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.18,0:14:04.33,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱下来～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.14,0:14:03.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰箱里的食物要额外算钱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.05,0:14:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:06.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.14,0:14:08.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.60,0:14:09.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.32,0:14:14.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天宫同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.18,0:14:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快脱掉…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.54,0:14:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好难受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.58,0:14:33.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:34.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.37,0:14:35.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.58,0:14:41.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一回圣樱学园学生会潜水大赛的优胜者是学美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.89,0:14:50.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,115  快拨115！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.92,0:14:52.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是国内电报！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:57.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:14:59.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的  别睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要给我无缘无故就倒立
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.89,0:15:04.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把体育新闻关了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.48,0:15:06.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是会胖的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.86,0:15:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还轮不到你说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.62,0:15:12.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:16.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个总该存有目的意识吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:19.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会把举行合宿的原因给忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.38,0:15:19.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.58,0:15:21.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.59,0:15:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的合宿\N是为了迎接学园祭而使大家意识统一才举办的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.96,0:15:35.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…大家一起玩这个怎么样…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.06,0:15:40.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赞成～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.96,0:16:58.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学美？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.43,0:17:04.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾不能去带海景的西式旅馆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.35,0:17:10.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碧海蓝天和雪白的西式旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.18,0:17:12.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有可爱的阳台
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.96,0:17:15.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,针对这些条件做了选择而预订了旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.35,0:17:19.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本一定会有十分特别的回忆的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.16,0:17:36.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是学生小姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.38,0:17:38.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡不着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.25,0:17:43.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊  合宿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.94,0:17:44.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.13,0:17:46.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.24,0:17:49.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有这样的经验
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:50.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得好羡慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.03,0:17:51.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.00,0:17:54.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  我没上过高中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.17,0:17:56.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.83,0:17:59.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  却没有后悔过哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.49,0:18:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟继承这家旅馆是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.11,0:18:04.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话  还是尽早来这里好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.98,0:18:07.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这个时代这么做是被认可的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.38,0:18:08.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是个性急的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.03,0:18:12.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.89,0:18:21.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没想过有什么想做的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.90,0:18:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一无所长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.19,0:18:27.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像学美时常精神百倍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.53,0:18:30.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小睦很擅长体育
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.26,0:18:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运动神经也很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.06,0:18:34.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小桃也在报道部努力着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.05,0:18:37.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽学习很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.69,0:18:38.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也很聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.82,0:18:45.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样再想想我的话  就感觉被落下好远
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.62,0:18:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连未来的事都没有考虑过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.37,0:18:52.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是茫然地在高中读书…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.29,0:18:56.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:18:58.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.73,0:19:01.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是为了这个才去上高中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.72,0:19:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必心急啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.37,0:19:06.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做的事  不久之后就会找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:07.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.63,0:19:10.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去整理一下「菊之间」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.54,0:19:11.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  是我拉住她聊天的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.67,0:19:17.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是学生小姐您的错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.86,0:19:21.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子很久没和与自己同代的人聊天了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.70,0:19:26.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过能和朋友一起进行暑假旅行真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.36,0:19:27.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.20,0:19:30.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前也经常去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.53,0:19:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太吵了给店员惹了不少麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.32,0:19:37.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上还一起起劲地聊着心仪男生的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.08,0:19:41.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我本来想让那孩子去读高中的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.26,0:19:45.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那孩子无论怎样都想来这里帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.89,0:19:48.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么与其去读高中  还不如来这里帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.36,0:19:50.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也觉得这样可以就同意了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.12,0:19:57.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我认为去学校的意义\N不仅仅在于「找到自己想做的事」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.86,0:20:00.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.81,0:20:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.42,0:20:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不仅仅在于此」  是什么意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.49,0:20:11.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛  总有一天你也会明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.50,0:20:23.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去学校的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.25,0:20:24.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.83,0:20:28.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还不能理解这么深奥的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.32,0:20:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底该怎样去做  也得不出结论
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.60,0:20:37.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之现在满脑子想的全是学园祭的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.15,0:20:40.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.36,0:20:46.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得在这家旅馆也充满了很多特别的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.04,0:20:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是和大家在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.12,0:20:53.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要是也这么想就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.33,0:21:07.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假  能被理解成学生们的特权
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.06,0:21:09.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特殊的暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.99,0:21:12.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只属于学生的特殊时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.44,0:21:18.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个被叫做答案的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.75,0:21:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定就包含在这个影像中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.87,0:21:44.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.31,0:21:47.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是圣樱学园的樱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.87,0:21:51.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有些事想和您通电话谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.32,0:22:02.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请讲吧
